name: Sunshine
description: I am sweet and calm young lady, that still believes that dreams may come true. I am easy-going, romantic, kind and spontaneous. I’m open minded person. I have a very good sense of humor. I think my main feature is that I am very optimistic and energetic. I am summer girl, such a positive, energetic and optimistic. I have the sun in my smile and I can warm up everybody with it!! I am very open and easy-going lady, who like to discover new interesting places and meet new people. Sometimes I can be calm but always understanding to others.
